data.text: Update: ~17 hours after first dose, minimal injection site soreness. Still have complete function of my arm (and I slept on it last night)! No other side effects.
Update: ~5 hours after first dose, some injection site soreness but VERY minimal. Feeling a-okay!

3/ received my first dose!! Did not hurt at ALL!!! 
Very fortunate to be one of the first vaccinated! https://t.co/FpttlycNzq

2/ The majority of patients here that I’m aware of, work for infectious diseases in some aspect. There has been complaints regarding the wait time... I believe up to an hour. I have no issue with that, but I’ve also only been here for 20 minutes.
